title: [RFC] Document the crate addition process
body:
In order to be able to review all new crates directly from the rust-vmm organization I propose that we go through the following steps:

1. Open an issue for adding a new crate to the rust-vmm project
2. If the crate gets accepted, a new, empty repository is created.
3. PRs against the new repo can be submitted, reviews can happen there.
